📤 [Data Submission Guide]

Please upload your country's dataset in the `/submissions/` folder.

- File format: `.csv`, `.rds`, `.xlsx`, or `.json`
- File name: `<Country>_<Description>.<ext>` (e.g., `Bangladesh_Census.csv`)
- If you prefer your data to be visible only to instructors, please email us directly or indicate in the file comment.

📁 [Optional Template]
You can use the sample file in `/templates/sample_format.csv` for reference.
